# RabbitMQ-Test-Tool

![Lint](https://github.com/nicolasbock/rabbitmq-tools/workflows/CI/badge.svg)
![Publish Python Package](https://github.com/nicolasbock/rabbitmq-test-tool/workflows/Publish%20Python%20Package/badge.svg)
